k\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n7. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n8. 保持<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立思考</span>，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour ，五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">低消費</span>，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">做孝子救港</span>，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆</span>貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF都買美股<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會事務，做陪審員、派傳單、放映會<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.10"},{"pid":"7d3de067f831cd2e73232ea9f9bf20e298903e23","tid":1557413,"uid":134054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:20:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">要諗方法應對 黑警不克制同主動撩事鬥非<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"185b2f8943ab2b28fd4430cec9dadb46bcf02f7b","tid":1557413,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:48:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74457e264f63ec7f6d3aba19f39742879e1e97ee","tid":1557413,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:06:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13bf36e14919f6a78ad59bb7a97a22f8c4c80c9a","tid":1557413,"uid":91230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:24:06.000Z","msg":"[2百萬人再集結] 915民陣大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1558668\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1558668</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n第一次整文宣 唔好屌咁大力 915民陣大遊行！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1558470\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1558470</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n大家跟我講，915民陣遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1558598\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1558598</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n915民陣 915民陣 915民陣 915民陣<br />\n<a hre